---
title: Italian-Style Lamb Ragu with Fusilli & Parmesan
description: This sumptuous yet simple pasta is absolute decadence. From the rich lamb ragu infused with Italian herbs to the topping of herby parsley and sharp grated Parmesan, don’t be too surprised if the bowls are licked clean!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-style-lamb-ragu-40a981fa.jpg
